            <span>• Omnichannel Journeys & Customer Experience</span>
            <span>• Customer Journey Management</span>
            <span>• DesignOps: Scaling UX Design & Research</span>
            <span>• Product and UX: Building Partnerships</span>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="transcript-section">
          <h3>Data Engineering & Analytics</h3>
